                        <i class="fas fa-heartbeat text-3xl mr-4 animate-pulse"></i>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Hipertensi (Tekanan Darah Tinggi)</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
                        <div class="md:w-1/2">
                            <img src="https://img.sanishtech.com/u/dd54256ece4b2a1800f32e9fedb8b972.png" alt="Hipertensi" class="rounded-lg shadow-md w-full h-64 object-cover animate-zoom-in">
                            
                            <!-- Ilustrasi Hipertensi dengan Animasi -->
                            <div class="medical-illustration h-64 flex items-center justify-center bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 dark:from-slate-700 dark:to-slate-600 rounded-lg relative overflow-hidden">
                                <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
                                    <i class="fas fa-heart text-6xl text-red-500 heart-animation"></i>
                                    <div class="absolute w-32 h-32 border-4 border-red-300 rounded-full animate-ping opacity-75"></div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-0 right-0 text-center">
                                    <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary">Hipertensi</h4>
                                    <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Tekanan Darah Tinggi</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- Animasi Tekanan Darah -->
                            <div class="mt-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 dark:from-slate-700 dark:to-slate-600 rounded-xl p-4 shadow-md interactive-element">
                                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3 flex items-center">
                                    <i class="fas fa-wave-square mr-2"></i> Simulator Tekanan Darah
                                </h4>
                                <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-4">
                                    <div class="text-center">
                                        <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary" id="systolic-value">120</div>
                                        <div class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Sistolik</div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="text-2xl text-slate-400">/</div>
                                    <div class="text-center">
                                        <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary" id="diastolic-value">80</div>
                                        <div class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Diastolik</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex space-x-2 mb-4">
                                    <button class="flex-1 bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-300 dark:hover:bg-slate-600 py-2 rounded-lg transition-colors" id="decrease-bp">↓ Turunkan</button>
                                    <button class="flex-1 bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-300 dark:hover:bg-slate-600 py-2 rounded-lg transition-colors" id="increase-bp">↑ Naikkan</button>
                                </div>
                                <div id="bp-status" class="text-center font-bold text-green-600">Normal</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="md:w-1/2">
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Apa itu Hipertensi?</h4>
                            <p class="mb-4">Hipertensi adalah kondisi medis kronis dimana tekanan darah di arteri meningkat secara terus-menerus. Tekanan darah normal adalah di bawah 120/80 mmHg, sementara hipertensi didefinisikan sebagai tekanan darah 140/90 mmHg atau lebih tinggi.</p>
                            
                            <!-- Grafik Tekanan Darah -->
                            <div class="mb-6 bg-white dark:bg-slate-700 rounded-lg p-4 shadow-md">
                                <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-primary mb-3">Klasifikasi Tekanan Darah</h4>
                                <div class="space-y-3">
                                    <div class="flex items-center">
                                        <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500 mr-2"></div>
                                        <span class="flex-1">Normal: < 120/80 mmHg</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="flex items-center">
                                        <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500 mr-2"></div>
                                        <span class="flex-1">Prehipertensi: 120-139/80-89 mmHg</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="flex items-center">
                                        <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-orange-500 mr-2"></div>
                                        <span class="flex-1">Hipertensi Stadium 1: 140-159/90-99 mmHg</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="flex items-center">
                                        <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500 mr-2"></div>
                                        <span class="flex-1">Hipertensi Stadium 2: ≥ 160/100 mmHg</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Faktor Risiko</h4>
                            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mb-4 space-y-2">
                                <li>Riwayat keluarga dengan hipertensi</li>
                                <li>Usia di atas 65 tahun</li>
                                <li>Kelebihan berat badan atau obesitas</li>
                                <li>Kurang aktivitas fisik</li>
                                <li>Konsumsi garam berlebihan</li>
                                <li>Konsumsi alkohol berlebihan</li>
                                <li>Stres kronis</li>
                            </ul>
                            
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Pencegahan dan Manajemen</h4>
                            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mb-4 space-y-2">
                                <li>Pola makan DASH (Dietary Approaches to Stop Hypertension)</li>
                                <li>Membatasi asupan natrium hingga kurang dari 2.300 mg/hari</li>
                                <li>Aktivitas fisik teratur (150 menit/minggu intensitas sedang)</li>
                                <li>Mempertahankan berat badan sehat</li>
                                <li>Membatasi konsumsi alkohol</li>
                                <li>Berhenti merokok</li>
                                <li>Manajemen stres</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/30 p-4 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-primary mt-6 mx-6 mb-6">
                        <p class="text-sm"><strong>Referensi:</strong> Whelton PK, et al. 2017 ACC/AHA/AAPA/ABC/ACPM/AGS/APhA/ASH/ASPC/NMA/PCNA Guideline for the Prevention, Detection, Evaluation, and Management of High Blood Pressure in Adults. Journal of the American College of Cardiology. 2018;71(19):e127-e248.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
